<%
  const breadcrumbs = [
    { name: "Home", href: "/" },
    { name: "Renault Magnum Truck Hearse", href: "/renault-magnum-hearse" }
  ];
%>

<%- include('partials/head', {
  title,
  metaTitle: 'Renault Magnum Truck Hearse Hire UK | PNW Carriage Masters',
  metaDescription: 'Discover our Renault Magnum truck hearse for funerals across the UK. A distinctive alternative hearse for a personal and memorable final journey.',
  canonicalPath,
  breadcrumbs
}) %>

<%- include('partials/header') %>

<%
  const s = settings || {};
  const phoneRaw = String(s.phone || "").trim();
  const phoneTel = phoneRaw.replace(/\s+/g, "");
  const renaultFile = String(s.renault_magnum_img || "").trim();
  const renaultVer  = String(s.renault_magnum_ver || "").trim();
%>

<div class="wrap">
<%- include('partials/breadcrumbs', { breadcrumbs }) %>
  <div class="card">
    <h1 style="color: var(--accent);">Renault Magnum Truck Hearse</h1>
    <p class="lead">
      Our Renault Magnum truck hearse is a distinctive specialist funeral vehicle, available as part of our bespoke
      alternative funeral transport service across the UK mainland.
    </p>

    <div class="cta" style="margin:18px 0 8px;">
      <a class="btn" href="/contact">Enquire about this hearse</a>
      <a class="btn" href="/gallery">View gallery</a>
      <a class="btn" href="/case-studies">Case studies</a>
      <% if (phoneTel) { %>
        <a class="btn" href="tel:<%= phoneTel %>">Call <%= phoneRaw %></a>
      <% } %>
    </div>
  </div>

  <% if (renaultFile) { %>
  <div class="card" style="margin-top:20px;">
    <img
      src="/uploads/<%= renaultFile %>?v=<%= renaultVer %>"
      alt="Renault Magnum truck hearse available for funeral hire across the UK"
      style="display:block; width:100%; max-width:560px; margin:0 auto; border-radius:16px;"
    >
  </div>
<% } %>

<div class="card" style="margin-top:20px;">
  <h2 class="section-title" style="color: var(--accent);">Technical specifications</h2>
  <div class="rich">
    <p><strong style="color: var(--accent);">Model:</strong> Renault Magnum Mk 2</p>
    <p><strong style="color: var(--accent);">Year of manufacture:</strong> 2005</p>
    <p><strong style="color: var(--accent);">Colour:</strong> Midnight Grey</p>
    <p><strong style="color: var(--accent);">Engine:</strong> Volvo 12 litre</p>
    <p><strong style="color: var(--accent);">Transmission:</strong> Auto I-Drive</p>
    <p><strong style="color: var(--accent);">Hearse conversion:</strong> 2024</p>
    <p style="margin-bottom:0;">
      <strong style="color: var(--accent);">Additional extras:</strong>
      Super singles fitted to front, Air horns, External music system, Bespoke aluminium body, Factory side skirts.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>

  <div class="card" style="margin-top:20px;">
    <h2 class="section-title" style="color: var(--accent);">A specialist Renault Magnum truck hearse</h2>
    <div class="rich">
      <p>
        The Renault Magnum truck hearse is chosen for funerals where families want a final journey with real character,
        presence and individuality. It offers a distinctive alternative to a conventional hearse while still delivering
        the dignity, care and professionalism expected on the day of the funeral.
      </p>
      <p>
        For many families, the vehicle becomes an important part of the tribute itself. Rather than simply choosing
        something different, they are choosing something that feels right for the person being remembered.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="card" style="margin-top:20px;">
    <h2 class="section-title" style="color: var(--accent);">Who this hearse often suits</h2>
    <div class="rich">
      <p>
        The Renault Magnum can be especially fitting for someone who worked in haulage, transport, logistics, recovery,
        engineering, plant, road haulage or heavy vehicles, or who simply had a lifelong connection with trucks and road life.
      </p>
      <p>
        It is often chosen when a family wants the funeral vehicle to reflect the person’s working life, interests, identity
        or character in a way that a traditional hearse may not.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="card" style="margin-top:20px;">
    <h2 class="section-title" style="color: var(--accent);">Why families choose the Renault Magnum</h2>
    <div class="rich">
      <p>
        Families choose this hearse when they want a more personal and memorable final journey. The Renault Magnum creates
        a striking impression while remaining respectful and appropriate to the occasion.
      </p>
      <p>
        It can help the funeral feel more fitting for someone whose life was closely tied to the road, and for many families
        that added sense of relevance and individuality is what makes the tribute feel complete.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="card" style="margin-top:20px;">
    <h2 class="section-title" style="color: var(--accent);">What to expect on the day</h2>
    <div class="rich">
      <p>
        Our Renault Magnum truck hearse is supplied to work alongside the funeral director and the wider arrangements
        already in place for the service. The aim is always to provide a vehicle that complements the funeral professionally,
        respectfully and with the right presence for the day.
      </p>
      <p>
        We understand that timing, route, venue access and the overall tone of the service all matter. The Renault Magnum
        is provided as part of a dignified final journey, not simply as a display vehicle.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="card" style="margin-top:20px;">
    <h2 class="section-title" style="color: var(--accent);">Working with funeral directors</h2>
    <div class="rich">
      <p>
        Our specialist hearses are supplied exclusively for the funeral profession. We work with funeral directors to confirm
        availability, discuss the location and service details, and help ensure the chosen vehicle is suitable for the funeral plans.
      </p>
      <p>
        This helps give funeral directors and families confidence that the Renault Magnum truck hearse will be a fitting and
        dependable part of the day’s arrangements.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="card" style="margin-top:20px;">
    <h2 class="section-title" style="color: var(--accent);">Available for funerals across the UK</h2>
    <div class="rich">
      <p>
        Our Renault Magnum truck hearse is available for funeral hire across the UK mainland. We are based near Chester,
        close to North Wales and North West England, but can provide specialist truck hearse hire much further afield,
        depending on the date, the location and the vehicle required.
      </p>
      <p>
        For availability, coverage and guidance on the most suitable option for a funeral, please contact us directly.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="card" style="margin-top:20px;">
    <h2 class="section-title" style="color: var(--accent);">Related gallery and case studies</h2>
    <div class="rich">
      <p>
        You can explore more Renault Magnum images on our <a href="/gallery">gallery page</a> and view recent field updates
        on our <a href="/case-studies">case studies page</a>.
      </p>
      <p>
        These pages help show how our specialist hearses are used in real funeral settings and how a truck hearse can become
        a meaningful part of a personal final journey.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="card" style="margin-top:20px;">
    <h2 class="section-title" style="color: var(--accent);">Frequently asked questions about this hearse</h2>
    <div class="rich">
      <p><strong>Is the Renault Magnum available across the UK?</strong><br>
        Yes. Availability depends on the date, the location and the overall funeral arrangements, so early enquiry is always helpful.
      </p>
      <p><strong>Who usually books this hearse?</strong><br>
        The vehicle is supplied for the funeral profession and is typically arranged as part of the funeral director’s plans for the service.
      </p>
      <p><strong>Is it suitable instead of a traditional hearse?</strong><br>
        In many cases, yes. Families often choose it when they want a more personal tribute that reflects the life, work or interests of the person being remembered.
      </p>
      <p style="margin-bottom:0;"><strong>Where can I find out more?</strong><br>
        You can also visit our <a href="/faq">FAQ page</a> or contact us directly to discuss availability and suitability.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="card" style="margin-top:20px;">
    <h2 class="section-title">Related pages</h2>
    <div class="rich">
      <p><a href="/erf-ec12-hearse">ERF EC12 hearse</a></p>
      <p><a href="/lorry-hearse-hire-uk">Lorry hearse hire across the UK</a></p>
      <p><a href="/truck-hearse-vs-traditional-hearse">Truck hearse vs traditional hearse</a></p>
      <p><a href="/case-studies">Truck hearse case studies</a></p>
      <p><a href="/gallery">Gallery</a></p>
      <p><a href="/faq">FAQ</a></p>
      <p><a href="/contact">Contact</a></p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="card" style="margin-top:20px;">
    <h2 class="section-title" style="color: var(--accent);">Enquire about the Renault Magnum truck hearse</h2>
    <div class="rich">
      <p>
        If you would like to discuss availability, location or whether the Renault Magnum is the right fit for an upcoming funeral,
        please contact us directly.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="cta" style="margin:18px 0 0;">
      <a class="btn" href="/contact">Contact us</a>
      <a class="btn" href="/gallery">View gallery</a>
      <a class="btn" href="/case-studies">View case studies</a>
      <% if (phoneTel) { %>
        <a class="btn" href="tel:<%= phoneTel %>">Call <%= phoneRaw %></a>
      <% } %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>
